query_1_sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM transactions WHERE user_id = 'U001' AND amount > 100000 AND timestamp < '2025-08-01 17:55:10';
query_2_sql: SELECT transaction_id, amount, location, timestamp FROM transactions WHERE user_id = 'U001' AND amount > 100000 ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
query_3_sql: SELECT t.transaction_id, t.amount, t.location, t.timestamp, a.alert_type FROM transactions t JOIN alerts a ON t.transaction_id = a.transaction_id WHERE t.user_id = 'U001' AND a.alert_type = 'HighValue' ORDER BY t.timestamp DESC;
query_4_sql: SELECT l.timestamp, l.ip_address, l.device_id FROM login_attempts l WHERE l.user_id = 'U001' AND l.status = 'SUCCESS' AND l.timestamp < '2025-08-01 17:55:10' ORDER BY l.timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
query_5_sql: SELECT d.device_id, d.device_type, d.os, d.last_seen_ip FROM devices d JOIN user_devices ud ON d.device_id = ud.device_id WHERE ud.user_id = 'U001' AND d.last_seen_ip = 'Sudan';
query_6_sql: SELECT AVG(amount) as avg_amount, MAX(amount) as max_amount, COUNT(*) as txn_count FROM transactions WHERE user_id = 'U001' AND timestamp > date('now', '-90 days')
query_7_sql: SELECT * FROM transactions WHERE user_id = 'U001' AND amount > 100000
query_9_sql: SELECT * FROM transactions WHERE user_id = 'U001' ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
query_10_sql: SELECT * FROM login_attempts WHERE user_id = 'U001' ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
query_12_sql: SELECT d.* FROM devices d JOIN user_devices ud ON d.device_id = ud.device_id WHERE ud.user_id = 'U001';
